OL,3,CWest Sussex fire crews tackling fire
OL,4,Cat property in Haywards Heath
OL,6,FFire crews are the scene of a fire at
OL,7,Fa property in Haywards Heath.
OL,9,FFirefighters were called to a property
OL,10,Foff Southdowns Park in the early hours
OL,11,Fof Saturday. (25 April)
OL,13,FThe service says there are currently
OL,14,F10 fire engines in attendance.
OL,16,FA spokesperson for West Sussex Fire
OL,17,Fand Rescue said: "Residents living
OL,18,Fnearby should remain indoors with
OL,19,Ftheir doors and windows closed while
OL,20,Fthe fire is brought under control.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/2
